install_msg:
Thanks for installing Brainfuck! For info on this cog, use `,help CogName`! 
If you want to help translate, go to my [crowdin](https://crowdin.com/project/Star-Cogs)
If you like my work, [donate me!](https://ko-fi.com/starcogs) 

To use it, either brainfuck something ([p]brainfuck <Text-input>), or Un-Brainfuck it ([p]unbrainfuck <Brainfuck-input>)!
